mple, were less concerned with the\ndetails of understanding an algorithmic calculation than with who or what is\njudging the result of the algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2020 20:06:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-22"}
