om a slow, wide-angle wind\nthat has not lost completely the Keplerian signature from its launching region.\nWe sketch an evolutionary scenario that could explain the combined [OI] and\n[NeII] results and includes screening of hard (~1keV) X-rays in inner, mostly\nmolecular, MHD winds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2020 22:56:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
